 violet;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">由此可見，肥鳩大隻同本癲狗實力縣殊，想借本癲狗上位卻慘敗收場，因而只能作出零星而無力的反抗，反過來誣衊本癲狗借佢條傻鳩上位，其實本癲狗只係從容撚狗，已獲得大家支持</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>同時亦證明左，無論肥鳩大隻花盡心機，唸盡辦法想同本癲狗玩，但換黎既結果只有慘敗同被撚，所以永遠活係本癲狗既陰影之下<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"a175a6091b721e1db2e43eada7e1060f3bd65a8b","tid":462091,"uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T09:02:14.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: pink;\">當肥鳩大隻被拆穿其柒點時，就會以話自己&ldquo;假膠&rdquo;同話對方&ldquo;真心膠&rdquo;來為自己辯護，如下圖:</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s26.postimg.org/huoj9jqeh/Screenshot_2017-09-29-14-11-56.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs26.postimg.org%2Fhuoj9jqeh%2FScreenshot_2017-09-29-14-11-56.png&h=0f10322e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n可惜條傻鳩唔明白一個道理，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">就係明眼人一睇就知，肥鳩其實就係故事主角既投射</span></span></strong>，例如牠本身又肥又矮，就會引用d主角又肥又矮既故事。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\"><strong>所以各位都爭相留下正皮，表示對其恥笑及支持本癲狗的撚狗行為<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"4c3f9f5115f264f51bbcedb1bf0235b099fbb0b1","tid":462091,"uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T09:03:49.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">文盲牛屎佬肥鳩大隻回覆親post呃正評都要趁連登各位巴打打錯字但自己卻打錯字，永遠都活喺本癲狗同連登各位巴打陰影之下<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s26.postimg.org/wx6ks9uq1/1505721362017.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs26.postimg.org%2Fwx6ks9uq1%2F1505721362017.png&h=31f16109&s={SIZ